# ── Build output ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# compiled binaries: bin/aphelion, bin/aphelion-static
# anchored to repo root so nested tracked bin/ dirs (e.g. external-tools/*/bin) stay tracked
/bin/
.cache/

# ── Go ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# `go test` compiled binaries + coverage/profiles
*.test
*.out
coverage.out
coverage.html
*.cover
*.coverprofile
*.prof
*.pprof
# delve debugger binaries
__debug_bin*
# local-only multi-module workspaces
go.work
go.work.sum

# ── Generated outputs ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generated local eval/release outputs. Promote curated public artifacts to docs/.
reports/
docs/architecture/diagrams/generated/*
!docs/architecture/diagrams/generated/README.md
# _spec/ holds PlantUML sources only; rendered diagrams are generated, not committed
_spec/**/*.svg

# ── Runtime / local agent state ───────────────────────────────────
# runtime home: config, memory archives, sqlite
.aphelion/
# local Claude Code config + skills symlink
.claude/

# ── Secrets & local config (repo is scanned by gitleaks) ──────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
# local config overrides — config.example.toml stays tracked
*.local.toml
# real runtime config — keep bot tokens out of git
aphelion.toml
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.token
*-credentials.json

# ── Editors / IDEs ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.bak
# merge/patch leftovers
*.orig
*.rej

# ── macOS / OS cruft ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ── Logs & temp ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
logs/
tmp/
.tmp/
*.tmp
